OL,3,CStarmer to chair Cobra as energy bills
OL,4,Cpredicted to rise by nearly #300
OL,6,FSir Keir Starmer is set to chair a
OL,7,Fmeeting of the Cobra crisis committee
OL,8,Fas the cost to households from the war
OL,9,Fin Iran became clearer, with future
OL,10,Frises in energy bills predicted for UK
OL,11,Fhouseholds.
OL,13,FAverage energy bills are forecast to
OL,14,Frise by almost #300 from July, while
OL,15,Fmotorists are already counting the
OL,16,Fcost of the war, with drivers paying
OL,17,F#544 million extra for fuel since the
OL,18,Fconflict in the Middle East began.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
