FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1774987556
OL,3,CStarmer to chair Cobra as energy bills
OL,4,Cpredicted to rise by nearly #300
OL,6,FThe prime minister said the Cobra
OL,7,Fmeeting will look at "making sure that
OL,8,Feverything that we need to have in
OL,9,Fplace" to respond to the crisis is set
OL,10,Fup.
OL,12,FThe price most households pay for
OL,13,Fenergy under regulator Ofgem's cap
OL,14,Fwill fall by #117-a-year to #1,641
OL,15,Ffrom Wednesday, driven by the
OL,16,Fgovernment's promise to cut bills by
OL,17,Fan average of #150 by removing green
OL,18,Fsubsidies.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1774987556
OL,3,CStarmer to chair Cobra as energy bills
OL,4,Cpredicted to rise by nearly #300
OL,6,FEnergy analyst Cornwall Insight said
OL,7,Fits prediction for the watchdog's
OL,8,Fprice cap from July to September now
OL,9,Fstands at #1,929 for a typical dual
OL,10,Ffuel household ` an increase of #288
OL,11,For 18% on April's cap.
OL,13,FChancellor Rachel Reeves has already
OL,14,Findicated that "targeted" help for
OL,15,Fpoorer households could be available
OL,16,Fif bills continue to rise, with
OL,17,Fparticular worries in government about
OL,18,Fthe impact in the autumn when energy
OL,19,Fuse increases as temperatures drop.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1774987556
OL,3,CStarmer to chair Cobra as energy bills
OL,4,Cpredicted to rise by nearly #300
OL,6,FHer reassurances of support appeared
OL,7,Fto rule out a more expensive universal
OL,8,Fapproach, the likes of which were seen
OL,9,Funder Liz Truss' government when the
OL,10,Fwar in Ukraine caused a spike in
OL,11,Fenergy prices.
OL,13,FThe costs for homes reliant on heating
OL,14,Foil, which are not covered by the
OL,15,FOfgem cap, have already soared.
OL,17,FThe government has announced a #53
OL,18,Fmillion package of support for these
OL,19,Fcustomers.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
