CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1774987556
OL,3,CStarmer to chair Cobra as energy bills
OL,4,Cpredicted to rise by nearly #300
OL,6,FThe impact of the Strait of Hormuz
OL,7,Fblockade has been compounded by Iran-
OL,8,Fbacked Houthis in Yemen launching
OL,9,Fstrikes against Israel, raising the
OL,10,Fpossibility of attacks on Red Sea
OL,11,Fshipping.
OL,13,FDiesel prices have reached their most
OL,14,Fexpensive level since December 2022,
OL,15,Fwith the average price of a litre of
OL,16,Fthe fuel at UK forecourts on Monday
OL,17,Fhitting 182.8p according to RAC
OL,18,Fanalysis.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31306
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1774987556
OL,3,CStarmer to chair Cobra as energy bills
OL,4,Cpredicted to rise by nearly #300
OL,6,FThat represents a 28% increase from
OL,7,F142.4p on February 28, the day the war
OL,8,Fin the Middle East began.
OL,10,FAverage petrol prices have reached
OL,11,F152.0p per litre, a rise of 14% from
OL,12,F132.8p over the same period.
OL,14,FStarmer has previously promised to
OL,15,Fkeep a planned rise in fuel duty from
OL,16,FSeptember "under review in light of
OL,17,Fwhat's happening in Iran", and the
OL,18,Fgovernment has stepped up efforts to
OL,19,Fhelp drivers find the cheapest fuel in
OL,20,Ftheir area through a price comparison
OL,21,Fapp.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
