OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1774987556
OL,3,CStarmer to chair Cobra as energy bills
OL,4,Cpredicted to rise by nearly #300
OL,6,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,7,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,8,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,9,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,11,FSpeaking on a Tuesday visit to
OL,12,FHertfordshire, Conservative leader
OL,13,FKemi Badenoch said the Tories would
OL,14,Fcut VAT on energy bills for three
OL,15,Fyears and scrap "unnecessary" green
OL,16,Flevies.
OL,18,F"It'll be a lot better for them to get
OL,19,Fthe money by drilling oil and gas in
OL,20,Fthe North Sea and using those revenues
OL,21,Fto cover the cost," she said.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31308
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1774987556
OL,3,CStarmer to chair Cobra as energy bills
OL,4,Cpredicted to rise by nearly #300
OL,6,F"And of course, the Government needs
OL,7,Fto stop the planned rise in fuel duty
OL,8,Fin September. With everything that's
OL,9,Fgoing on, the last thing the
OL,10,FGovernment needs is to increase the
OL,11,Fcost of living for hard-working
OL,12,Ffamilies."
OL,14,FAhead of the Cobra meeting, Starmer
OL,15,Fwelcomed Syrian President Ahmed al-
OL,16,FSharaa to Downing Street while Defence
OL,17,FSecretary John Healey is in the Middle
OL,18,FEast to speak to the UK's allies in
OL,19,Fthe Gulf.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
