OL,3,CStarmer to chair Cobra as energy bills
OL,4,Cpredicted to rise by nearly #300
OL,6,FThe US president has continued to
OL,7,Finsist that "great progress" has been
OL,8,Fmade in talks with Iran, negotiations
OL,9,Fthat Iran continues to deny the
OL,10,Fexistence of.
OL,12,FTrump has simultaneously warned that,
OL,13,Funless the Strait of Hormuz is opened
OL,14,Fto shipping, the US will respond by
OL,15,F"completely obliterating" Iran's power
OL,16,Fplants and oil wells.
OL,18,FHe also raised the prospect of
OL,19,Fattacking desalination plants, which
OL,20,Fprovide drinking water to Iranian
OL,21,Fcitizens.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/10
